This is Lieutenant Ivan Burnett.
He's from San Quentin.

2029
02:25:54.729 --> 02:25:57.357
- Detective Paco Aguilar. How ya doin'? Yeah.
- This the victim?

2030
02:25:58.600 --> 02:26:00.568
Paco. we just heard
from Sacramento.

2031
