No. but my warden has
and he's Chicano.

2053
02:27:05.867 --> 02:27:08.700
Well. is your warden related
to someone on the Onda council?

2054
02:27:08.770 --> 02:27:11.762
Miklo Velka is my...
is my cousin.

2055
02:27:11.840 --> 02:27:14.832
